@startuml

title Diagrama de Secuencia - Flujo de cálculo de descuento

skinparam wrapWidth 250
skinparam maxMessageSize 100

actor FrontEnd
participant SalesEndpoints
participant CalculateDiscountPipeline
participant SaleContext
participant SearchOrCreateCustomerHandler
participant CreateSaleHandler
participant ApplyDiscountHandler

FrontEnd -> SalesEndpoints : POST /v1/sales/discount\n(SaleRequest)
activate SalesEndpoints

SalesEndpoints -> CalculateDiscountPipeline : HandleRequest(request)
activate CalculateDiscountPipeline

CalculateDiscountPipeline -> SaleContext ** : new SaleContext\n{ SaleRequest = request }

CalculateDiscountPipeline -> SearchOrCreateCustomerHandler : HandleAsync(context)
activate SearchOrCreateCustomerHandler
SearchOrCreateCustomerHandler --> SaleContext : CustomerEntity, IsNewCustomer
SearchOrCreateCustomerHandler -> CreateSaleHandler : HandleAsync(context)
deactivate SearchOrCreateCustomerHandler

activate CreateSaleHandler
CreateSaleHandler --> SaleContext : SaleEntity
CreateSaleHandler -> ApplyDiscountHandler : HandleAsync(context)
deactivate CreateSaleHandler

activate ApplyDiscountHandler
ApplyDiscountHandler --> SaleContext : SaleDiscount
note over ApplyDiscountHandler
    No hay siguiente handler:
    la cadena termina aquí sin persistir
end note
deactivate ApplyDiscountHandler

CalculateDiscountPipeline --> SalesEndpoints : context
deactivate CalculateDiscountPipeline

SalesEndpoints --> FrontEnd : 200 OK\n(SaleResultDto sin SaleId)
deactivate SalesEndpoints

@enduml
